        <ReportItem id="q1" type="Radio" blobItem="Q1" blobType="BLOB_TEXT" options="a. Avoid doing physical activity|b. Wear safe footwear indoors and outdoors|c. Adapt your space to your needs|d. Both answers b. and c.">
            <![CDATA[
                <h3>What can you do to avoid the risk of falling?</h3>
                {$item}
            ]]>
        </ReportItem>
    </ReportSection>
    
    <!-- Answer 1 -->
    <ReportSection id="a1" tooltip="Answers1" name="Answer1" title="QUESTION 1" blobSection="QUIZ" type="QuizReportSection" hidden="true">
        <ReportItem id="q1" type="Answer" blobItem="Q1" blobType="BLOB_TEXT" label="Answer 1" answer="d. Both answers b. and c.">
            <![CDATA[
                {$item}
                <b>(wear safe footwear indoors and outdoors; adapt your space to your needs)</b>
                <p>Physical activity is one of the most important aspects of reducing your risk of falls, especially when it comes to improving your balance. However, it’s not the only thing you can do. Wearing appropriate footwear and adapting your space will lower your risk for falling.</p>
                    
                <p>Be sure to check out the education resources for more detailed information on these steps.</p>
            ]]>
        </ReportItem>
    </ReportSection>
    
    <!-- Question 2 -->
