            <![CDATA[
                <h3>Vision is related to falls prevention</h3>
                {$item}
            ]]>
        </ReportItem>
    </ReportSection>
    
    <!-- Answer 2 -->
    <ReportSection id="a2" tooltip="Answers" name="Answer2" title="QUESTION 2" blobSection="QUIZ" type="QuizReportSection" hidden="true">
        <ReportItem id="q2" type="Answer" blobItem="Q2" blobType="BLOB_TEXT" label="Answer 2" answer="True">
            <![CDATA[
                {$item}
                <b>The truth is, if you can’t see well, your risk for falling increases.</b>
                <p>
                    A decreased sharpness in vision, an inability to distinguish between shades, problems with glare, and slower adaption to darkness can occur with age. Some age-related eye diseases increase risk for falling, as do dimly lit rooms.
                </p>
            ]]>
        </ReportItem>
    </ReportSection>
    
