            <![CDATA[
                {$item}
                <b>The truth is, if you are scared of falling and stop moving your body, your risk increases. But one fall isn’t indicative of another one.</b>
                <p>If you continue to be cognizant of the risks, you can put forth the effort to prevent falling. Remember that exercise is the best defence for falls prevention.</p>
